7. Upgrade Validation

Before upgrade execution:

The system validates:

- device reachability
- supported platform
- current version
- target version compatibility
- image availability

Validation failures immediately terminate workflow.

---

8. API Design

Endpoint

PUT /nosupdate/upgrade

---

Request Parameters

Parameter| Description
deviceId| Target device
currentVersion| Existing version
targetVersion| Upgrade version
imageUrl| Upgrade image URL
upgradeType| Upgrade mode

---

Response

Field| Description
requestId| Workflow ID
status| Upgrade status
message| Operation result

---

9. Upgrade States

State| Description
REQUESTED| Upgrade requested
VALIDATING| Validation running
STAGED| Image prepared
IN_PROGRESS| Upgrade executing
REBOOTING| Device rebooting
VERIFYING| Post-upgrade verification
SUCCESS| Upgrade successful
FAILED| Upgrade failed

